title: 285. Andy & DJ CTI: Former MO Rep. Dies Of Heart Condition, Nina Jankowicz’s Mary Poppins TikTok & Netflix Begins Layoffs
itunes:title: 285. Andy & DJ CTI: Former MO Rep. Dies Of Heart Condition, Nina Jankowicz’s Mary Poppins TikTok & Netflix Begins Layoffs
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss former Missouri Rep. Cora Faith Walker passing away due to a heart condition at the age of 37, Biden's “disinfo” czar Nina Jankowicz being ripped over her cringeworthy Mary Poppins TikTok, and Netflix laying off employees after stock shares crater 25% for the first time in 10 years.
